Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:10.28,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C'é il mare etarno nella mia anima
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:16.58,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ovunque tu vada
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:22.86,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ovunque io vada
